properties.markdownProperty:
If you want to add children to the archetype or have nested children, you must create an XML file for every object. Add child to an object using the following syntax `<child id="5CpGMmY8bNrp"/>` inside the children tag, where `id` is the object identifier. Example archetype:
``` <?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?> <object id="5Xvf87GNZw2U" classes="section" acceptedChildren=":Proteus-any" acceptedParents=":Proteus-any"> <properties> <stringProperty name=":Proteus-name" category="general">Necesidades de negocio</stringProperty>
<markdownProperty name="comments" category="general"></markdownProperty> </properties> <children> <child id="5CpGMmY8bNrp"/> <child id="33mMboh8kCKe"/> </children> <traces/> </object> ```
